title: Creamy Tomato Spaghetti

! Ingredients
* fresh cream
* blanched and chopped tomatoes
* sun-dried tomatoes
* cherry tomatoes
* cooked spaghetti
* olive oil
* chopped garlic (lehsun)
* dry red chilli flakes (paprika)
* salt
* grated processed cheese
* freshly ground black pepper (kalimirch)
* grated processed cheese
* garlic bread

! Process
