* Add the chilli flakes, tomatoes and salt, mix well and cook on a medium flame for 3 to 4 minutes.
* Add the sun-dried tomatoes, cherry tomatoes, cheese, spaghetti and pepper powder, toss well and cook on medium flame for 2 minutes, while stirring occasionally.
* Garnish with cheese and serve immediately with garlic bread.
